text: Noored kotkad, also known as Young Eagles, is a 1927 Estonian adventure movie directed by Theodor Luts and starring Ruut Tarmo, Amalie Konsa, Aksella Luts. It was distributed by Taska Film. ==Other websites== * Category:1927 movies Category:Estonian movies Category:1920s adventure movies Category:Silent movies
